==Abduction and search effort==
In September 1990, Jaycee Dugard and her family moved from the [[Orange County, California|Orange County]] city of [[Garden Grove, California|Garden Grove]] to South Lake Tahoe. At the time of the abduction, Dugard was in fifth grade attending Meyers Elementary School near South Lake Tahoe.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5inzriL_5JLhSRHcaNTxW8Mh9PJVwD9AFLJ580 |title=Parade to mark return of Calif. kidnap victim|publisher=Associated Press |date= 2009-09-03}}</ref>
